summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2035 , for the improvement of Maple Leaf Place from 5th Avenue Northeast to 6th Avenue Northeast, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, by grading and regrading the same, with necessary appurtenances for the proper surface drainage of said district, under Ordinance No. 20440 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
